        "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/www.wineberserkers.com/max_k/{size}/2700_2.png",
        "created_at": "2017-11-08T01:48:43.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>These two vignerons are much admired - including by me - for their domaine wines. But they also have pretty extensive negoce businesses alongside their respective domaines, and the negoce wines are pretty aggressively priced, sometimes equal to or higher than the domaine wines. You\u2019d think they\u2019d get a fair amount of attention, but I don\u2019t see many tasting notes. Anyone have any experience or (informed) opinions on these wines? Are they worth the tariff, or trading on the quality of domaine wines?</p>",
        "post_number": 1,
        "post_type": 1,
        "posts_count": 13,
        "updated_at": "2022-06-03T01:36:15.214Z",
        "reply_count": 0,
