        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/b/3be4f8/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2017-11-08T02:45:01.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>I rolled the dice on a few mags of Fourrier 2013 Latricieres because they were on deep discount.  Never tried a single one of their negoce wines before, and no intention to touch these mags until 2035 or later\u2026so I\u2019ll check back with you then - lol!</p>\n<p>Cheers,<br>\nBlair</p>",
