        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/g/8baadc/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2017-11-08T08:06:28.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>I\u00b4ve tasted the 13s to 15s at Fourrier \u2026 and my impression was that the negociant wines were good but were slightly behind the domaine wines in quality and individuality \u2026 (lacking the \u201cextra-something\u201d \u2026) \u2026 however - if you can\u00b4t get the domaine bottlings \u2026 maybe better than nothing (if the prices are ok)</p>",
