        "created_at": "2017-11-08T15:04:20.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Yes, Fourrier Neg inferior. Just as the Van Canneyt.<br>\nFunny thing is that Van Canneyt negociant wines are very expensive compared to the Hudelot Noellat prices\u2026so not good QPR</p>",
