        "cooked": "<aside class=\"quote no-group\" data-username=\"A Songeur\">\n<div class=\"title\">\n<div class=\"quote-controls\"></div>\n A Songeur:</div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Yes, Fourrier Neg inferior. Just as the Van Canneyt.<br>\nFunny thing is that Van Canneyt negociant wines are very expensive compared to the Hudelot Noellat prices\u2026so not good QPR</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>Buying grapes is more expensive than farming them!</p>",
