        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/i/f05b48/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2017-11-08T16:34:49.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>I\u2019m definitely in the camp of \u201cnot worth the money\u201d, unfortunately. I want to like the wines, but the price of these wines often outpaces the Domaine wines, which is bizarre.</p>",
        "post_number": 12,
